<section class="cp-section" id="reviews">
  <div class="cp-container">

    <div class="cp-section-header">
      <span class="cp-eyebrow">Customer Reviews</span>
      <h2 class="cp-heading">What Sleepers Are Saying</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="cp-reviews__stars-row">
      <div class="cp-reviews__overall">4.9</div>
      <div class="cp-reviews__stars-display">★★★★★</div>
      <div class="cp-reviews__count">Based on 2,847 verified reviews</div>
    </div>

    <div class="cp-reviews__grid">

      <div class="cp-review-card">
        <div class="cp-review-card__stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p class="cp-review-card__body">
          "I've tried so many pillows over the years for my neck pain. Nothing worked until The Cloud™. After just three nights, I woke up without that stiff neck I've had for years. It's genuinely life-changing."
        </p>
        <div class="cp-review-card__author">
          <div class="cp-review-card__avatar">S</div>
          <div>
            <div class="cp-review-card__name">Sarah M.</div>
            <div class="cp-review-card__date">April 2025</div>
            <div class="cp-review-card__badge">
              <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
              Verified Purchase
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="cp-review-card">
        <div class="cp-review-card__stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p class="cp-review-card__body">
          "As a side sleeper, I always wake up with shoulder pain. This pillow has the wings that actually support my shoulder and keep my spine straight. My chiropractor was shocked at how much my posture improved."
        </p>
        <div class="cp-review-card__author">
          <div class="cp-review-card__avatar" style="background:#2a8c45;">J</div>
          <div>
            <div class="cp-review-card__name">James T.</div>
            <div class="cp-review-card__date">March 2025</div>
            <div class="cp-review-card__badge">
              <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
              Verified Purchase
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="cp-review-card">
        <div class="cp-review-card__stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p class="cp-review-card__body">
          "I run hot at night and every pillow I've had traps heat. The Cloud™ stays cool all night — no more flipping to the cold side. The adjustable height is a bonus, I removed one layer and it's perfect for me."
        </p>
        <div class="cp-review-card__author">
          <div class="cp-review-card__avatar" style="background:#8b2fa6;">A</div>
          <div>
            <div class="cp-review-card__name">Amara K.</div>
            <div class="cp-review-card__date">May 2025</div>
            <div class="cp-review-card__badge">
              <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
              Verified Purchase
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="cp-review-card">
        <div class="cp-review-card__stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p class="cp-review-card__body">
          "My husband and I both bought one. We're completely different sleepers — he's a back sleeper, I'm a stomach sleeper — and we both love it. Best investment we've made for our sleep in years."
        </p>
        <div class="cp-review-card__author">
          <div class="cp-review-card__avatar" style="background:#c4581a;">R</div>
          <div>
            <div class="cp-review-card__name">Rachel &amp; Dan P.</div>
            <div class="cp-review-card__date">February 2025</div>
            <div class="cp-review-card__badge">
              <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
              Verified Purchase
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="cp-review-card">
        <div class="cp-review-card__stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p class="cp-review-card__body">
          "I was sceptical — I've bought so many 'miracle pillows' that didn't deliver. This one actually does. The quality of the memory foam is noticeably different. Firm where it needs to be, soft everywhere else."
        </p>
        <div class="cp-review-card__author">
          <div class="cp-review-card__avatar" style="background:#1a5f8c;">M</div>
          <div>
            <div class="cp-review-card__name">Michael O.</div>
            <div class="cp-review-card__date">January 2025</div>
            <div class="cp-review-card__badge">
              <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
              Verified Purchase
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="cp-review-card">
        <div class="cp-review-card__stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p class="cp-review-card__body">
          "The pillow arrived beautifully packaged. The navy blue pillowcase looks premium. But what really matters is the sleep — and it delivers. I'm getting an extra hour of deep sleep according to my tracker."
        </p>
        <div class="cp-review-card__author">
          <div class="cp-review-card__avatar" style="background:#5a3a6b;">L</div>
          <div>
            <div class="cp-review-card__name">Lena V.</div>
            <div class="cp-review-card__date">April 2025</div>
            <div class="cp-review-card__badge">
              <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
              Verified Purchase
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

